OL,7,F"The government's recent expansion of
OL,8,Fthe attendance mentors programme and
OL,9,Fcurriculum review is welcome, as is
OL,10,Fthe education minister's focus on this
OL,11,Fissue. But school absence has now
OL,12,Fbecome endemic with parents often
OL,13,Fthinking it is not essential for
OL,14,Fchildren to attend school every day.
