OL,7,FPepe Di'Iasio, general secretary of
OL,8,Fthe Association of School and College
OL,9,FLeaders (ASCL), said: "While it is
OL,10,Fgreat news that absence rates are
OL,11,Flower overall, and schools deserve
OL,12,Fgreat credit for this, there is
OL,13,Fclearly much more work to do.
OL,15,F"Of particular concern is the fact
OL,16,Fthat more than 2% of all pupils are
OL,17,Fnow missing at least half their time
OL,18,Fin school. This rate has more than
OL,19,Fdoubled since the start of the
OL,20,Fpandemic and now equates to well over
OL,21,F150,000 pupils.
