OL,7,F"These children are missing out on a
OL,8,Fhuge chunk of vital learning and
OL,9,Fschools need support to help them
OL,10,Freturn to the classroom. This will
OL,11,Frequire investment in attendance
OL,12,Fsupport services to help identify the
OL,13,Freasons behind these prolonged
OL,14,Fabsences, and to work towards
OL,15,Fsolutions."
